<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Menú de Postres</title>

<style>

body{
font-family: Arial;
background:#2b2b2b;
color:white;
margin:0;
text-align:center;
}

header{
background:#ff4fa3;
padding:20px;
font-size:30px;
font-weight:bold;
}

.menu{
display:flex;
flex-wrap:wrap;
justify-content:center;
gap:20px;
padding:30px;
}

.card{
background:#1e1e1e;
width:240px;
border-radius:15px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 0 10px black;
transition:0.3s;
}

.card:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.card img{
width:100%;
height:160px;
object-fit:cover;
}

.content{
padding:15px;
}

.price{
color:#00ff88;
font-size:20px;
font-weight:bold;
}

button{
background:#ff4fa3;
border:none;
padding:10px 20px;
color:white;
border-radius:8px;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:10px;
}

button:hover{
background:#ff2a8c;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
🍰 MENÚ DE POSTRES
</header>

<div class="menu">

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578985545062-69928b1d9587">
<div class="content">
<h3>Pastel de Chocolate</h3>
<p>Pastel suave con chocolate derretido.</p>
<div class="price">$75 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488477181946-6428a0291777">
<div class="content">
<h3>Cheesecake</h3>
<p>Cheesecake cremoso con fresa.</p>
<div class="price">$80 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563805042-7684c019e1cb">
<div class="content">
<h3>Helado Artesanal</h3>
<p>Helado de vainilla con topping.</p>
<div class="price">$60 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505253716362-afaea1d3d1af">
<div class="content">
<h3>Donas Glaseadas</h3>
<p>Donas recién hechas con azúcar.</p>
<div class="price">$50 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551024506-0bccd828d307">
<div class="content">
<h3>Waffles Dulces</h3>
<p>Waffles con miel y frutas.</p>
<div class="price">$70 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601979031925-424e53b6caaa">
<div class="content">
<h3>Brownie</h3>
<p>Brownie caliente con chocolate.</p>
<div class="price">$65 MXN</div>
<button>Ordenar</button>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>v
